node.title: Flights, Auckland Airport lounge listed as locations of interest
node.description: A number of flights and Auckland Domestic Airport's regional lounge have been listed as close-contact locations of interest by the Ministry of Health.
node.content:
["A number of flights and Auckland Domestic Airport's regional lounge have been listed as close-contact locations of interest by the Ministry of Health.", "", "
Several Air New Zealand flights were listed as high risk locations of interest. Photo: AFP
", "In Auckland, other high risk locations included a sushi shop in Milford and an education organisation in Henderson.", "A Sikh temple in Hamilton and a cafe in Paeroa were also added as close-contact locations today.", "Today's new close-contact locations of interest are:", "Anyone who was present for these high risk exposure events is asked to self-isolate and get tested immediately.", "A Waiheke ferry service was listed as a close-contact location earlier today, but has since been downgraded to a casual contact location.", "For up to date information, check the Ministry of Health's website."]
